Detailed and comprehensive information on the occurrence of a large
number of diseases [in Switzerland, including rabies] can be gathered from
the Swiss animal disease monitoring system. The internet address of the
English version is:
<http://www.bvet.admin.ch/tsme/start.htm?go=weiter>

